{"questionId":"11815","questionHtml":"<p>&nbsp;Find the equation of this asymptote.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>As&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"t \\to \\infty {\\text{,}}\\,\\,x \\simeq 30t{e^{2t}}{\\text{,}}\\,\\,y \\simeq&nbsp; - 30t{e^{2t}}\">\n  <mi>t</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">→</mo>\n  <mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>≃</mo>\n  <mn>30</mn>\n  <mi>t</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>≃</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>30</mn>\n  <mi>t</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>so asymptote is <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y = - x\">\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11815","referenceCode":"EXM.3.AHL.TZ0.2f.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the equation of this asymptote.","paper":"3","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"f.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.17—Phase portrait"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}